1
00:00:04,150 --> 00:00:06,999
<i>♫ Nowhere to escape. ♫</i>

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,959
<i>♫ No bough to alight. ♫</i>

3
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:14,030
<i>♫ Retrograde with smile. ♫</i>

4
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:18,869
<i>♫ Never give in. ♫</i>

5
00:00:18,870 --> 00:00:23,950
<i>♫ Forget about the youth. ♫</i>

6
00:00:25,950 --> 00:00:28,919
<i>♫ I've never been afraid of loneliness. ♫</i>

7
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:31,789
<i>♫ I also shed the tears of regret. ♫</i>

8
00:00:31,790 --> 00:00:34,789
<i>♫ But my heart is still fiery-hot. ♫</i>

9
00:00:34,790 --> 00:00:37,839
<i>♫ To the distance. ♫</i>

10
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:40,909
<i>♫ The miserable past is like a dagger. ♫</i>

11
00:00:40,910 --> 00:00:43,719
<i>♫ Though my wings are broken, ♫</i>

12
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:49,840
<i>♫ I will keep flying. ♫</i>

13
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:56,199
<i>♫ Following the light, ♫</i>

14
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:58,359
<i>♫ I'll forget you. ♫</i>

15
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:04,159
<i>♫ The memory shaped my stubbornness. ♫</i>

16
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:07,359
<i>♫ By virtue of the light in the dark night, ♫</i>

17
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:10,309
<i>♫ I'll return it with a long ballad. ♫</i>

18
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:12,269
<i>♫ The river of life is under my feet. ♫</i>

19
00:01:12,270 --> 00:01:16,760
<i>♫ I don't regret my craziness. ♫</i>

20
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:32,699
The Long Ballad

21
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:41,759
Episode 27

22
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:44,840
<i>[Luoyang Office]</i>

23
00:02:00,559 --> 00:02:01,519
Xiao Wu.

24
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:06,919
Wait for me.

25
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,639
Xiao Wu, Xiao Wu.

26
00:02:20,519 --> 00:02:21,560
Wait for me.

27
00:02:22,799 --> 00:02:23,799
Don't leave me.

28
00:02:24,359 --> 00:02:25,320
Xiao Wu.

29
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,680
Xiao Wu.

30
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,759
Princess.

31
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,560
Princess.

32
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:39,960
Forgive me, please.

33
00:02:41,239 --> 00:02:43,518
Where is Xiao Wu?

34
00:02:43,519 --> 00:02:44,878
Where is Xiao Wu?

35
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:46,798
I've ordered them to bury Xiao Wu.

36
00:02:46,799 --> 00:02:47,639
Please rest at ease.

37
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,040
I just had a dream.

38
00:03:07,359 --> 00:03:09,320
In the dream, Xiao Wu is still alive.

39
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:13,998
But I don't know why he's running.

40
00:03:13,999 --> 00:03:17,840
He keeps running and doesn't want to come back to me.

41
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,279
Hao Du,

42
00:03:24,999 --> 00:03:27,040
is he still blaming me?

43
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:29,480
If not for me,

44
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:33,840
he wouldn't have been wounded and sick for long.

45
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,840
He'd have lived well.

46
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:52,599
I promised to give him a cart of rice.

47
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,159
I would take him to Chang'an

48
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:58,320
to see the blooming spring and picturesque landscape.

49
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:04,799
Now it's all gone.

50
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,519
Princess.

51
00:04:08,279 --> 00:04:09,639
He's gone with a smile.

52
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,519
He didn't blame you.

53
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,519
Don't be sad.

54
00:04:15,799 --> 00:04:19,320
See him with me tomorrow.

55
00:04:22,159 --> 00:04:24,119
I want to be by his side until the end.

56
00:04:24,879 --> 00:04:25,679
Princess.

57
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:28,480
Aren't you scared of me now?

58
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,040
After all these things,

59
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:35,719
I'm not scared of death.

60
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,360
You? I'm no scared.

61
00:04:41,719 --> 00:04:43,719
I was scared of many things in the past.

62
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:49,640
How ridiculous I was.

63
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:56,240
Heaven rewards the good.

64
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,639
I've been guided to you by this amulet.

65
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,958
Now I return it to you.

66
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,679
Wish it a blessing to you.

67
00:05:10,119 --> 00:05:11,958
Why do you have it?

68
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,839
It's a long story.

69
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,279
I found it in Hongyi Palace.

70
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:18,679
Maybe it's God's will.

71
00:05:19,719 --> 00:05:21,640
If God pities me,

72
00:05:23,159 --> 00:05:27,920
please bless the peace of all people.

73
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,320
Sure he will.

74
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:31,760
God bless Tang.

75
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,439
It's God's will.

76
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,200
Take it.

77
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:43,279
Hope it works till the end.

78
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,878
Please don't be upset.

79
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:48,118
Take care of yourself.

80
00:05:48,119 --> 00:05:50,158
I've ordered to find the servant you're most familiar with

81
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,159
to take care of you.

82
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:52,800
She'll be here soon.

83
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,320
Thanks a lot.

84
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:08,719
Honestly, it's very lucky for you to come here.

85
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:10,359
You know what?

86
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:13,278
Liuyun Taoist Temple is a blessed land in the world.

87
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:15,359
It's perfect with kindness and insight,

88
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:17,320
delivers all living creatures from difficulty.

89
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:20,040
You aren't listening to me, are you?

90
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,240
How rude this prentice is.

91
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:28,620
<i>[Yuqing's utmost Tao]</i>

92
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:39,220
<i>[Great virtues match the heaven and the earth.]</i>

93
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,998
Nice to meet you, Taoist Sun.

94
00:06:41,999 --> 00:06:43,158
Master has been talking about you.

95
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,480
Finally you're here.

96
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,158
Go to tell Master Taoist Sun's coming.

97
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:47,959
Okay.

98
00:06:49,119 --> 00:06:50,080
Let's go inside.

99
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,360
This lady is...

100
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,760
She was picked by me.

101
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:03,640
She's in a bad mood, touchy now.

102
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,920
Please come in.

103
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,480
Are you better now?

104
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,800
Eat something.

105
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,240
Eat it.

106
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,559
Slow down.

107
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,719
Here we help refugees.

108
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,959
They're very piteous.

109
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:41,159
We help the poor people.

110
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:43,759
This way.

111
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:58,039
Liuyun Taoist Temple is divided into three yards.

112
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,200
Front, middle and back.

113
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:03,639
This is the pharmacy, opposite Taoist Sun's exam room,

114
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:05,799
which is connected to the exam rooms in front yard.

115
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,520
This is where Master lives.

116
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:10,520
Let's go to backyard.

117
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,920
This is the backyard.

118
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,919
It's silent here with many rooms.

119
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,320
You can choose one to live.

120
00:08:30,679 --> 00:08:34,559
If you find yourself boring, come to me and A'Bi.

121
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:45,580
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

122
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:53,380
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

123
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:02,800
What are you looking at?

124
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,319
What is this place?

125
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,398
Master always meditates here.

126
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:09,680
We call it the silence room.

127
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:17,600
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

128
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,560
Shall I live here?

129
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:40,580
<i>[Dear Brother Xiao Wu]</i>

130
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,360
Princess.

131
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:14,120
Death is final.

132
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:15,880
My condolences.

133
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:21,638
Please don't blame yourself.

134
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,839
He has an unkind fate.

135
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:25,718
He took care of you a lot.

136
00:10:25,719 --> 00:10:26,959
He's a righteous man.

137
00:10:29,719 --> 00:10:31,838
If you can't reconcile with yourself,

138
00:10:31,839 --> 00:10:34,680
we can ask for a reward for him when we arrive in Chang'an.

139
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,799
He won't care about that.

140
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:44,120
Besides, he's gone.

141
00:10:44,839 --> 00:10:46,079
It's useless.

142
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:52,839
Hope one day everyone in Tang don't need to

143
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:56,519
suffer from war, coldness, hunger, homelessness, or misery.

144
00:10:57,440 --> 00:11:02,519
Hope everyone have food to eat, field to farm

145
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:08,399
with no theft or danger.

146
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,399
I think it's the halcyon days.

147
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:13,840
It will.

148
00:11:14,719 --> 00:11:15,959
We'll have that day.

149
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:34,959
Xiao Wu.

150
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,759
I'll eat this bowl of rice for you.

151
00:11:40,319 --> 00:11:44,839
You won't be hungry anymore with so much rice.

152
00:12:23,950 --> 00:12:26,120
<i>I'm not a disloyal man.</i>

153
00:12:29,070 --> 00:12:30,599
<i>I didn't recognize you.</i>

154
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,270
<i>I apologize to you for my sister.</i>

155
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:37,800
<i>With me, you can't be starving, can you?</i>

156
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:52,719
<i>[Dear Brother Xiao Wu]</i>

157
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:56,420
<i>[Luoyang Office]</i>

158
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,269
Finally you're here, Princess.

159
00:13:27,270 --> 00:13:29,189
I'm so worried about you.

160
00:13:29,190 --> 00:13:30,829
Thank God.

161
00:13:30,830 --> 00:13:32,879
Please take a bath and put on clean clothes.

162
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:34,190
I'll help you.

163
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:39,509
Why are you crying?

164
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:41,000
I'm okay now.

165
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:45,439
I'm so glad to see you, Princess.

166
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,919
Take a rest first.

167
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:47,830
I can do it myself.

168
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,280
But...

169
00:13:49,950 --> 00:13:50,880
I'm okay with that.

170
00:13:51,830 --> 00:13:52,749
Okay.

171
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:55,710
Call me anytime if you need me.

172
00:14:08,950 --> 00:14:11,359
Princess rests here tonight.

173
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,479
Keep your eyes open.

174
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,280
Yes, sir.

175
00:14:18,070 --> 00:14:18,870
Go.

176
00:14:20,070 --> 00:14:20,870
Stop.

177
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,240
Who's the commander?

178
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:34,879
What brings you here so late at night?

179
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:36,149
A royal warrant.

180
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:37,240
I dare not to waste time.

181
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:39,040
Please receive it, commander.

182
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:48,360
<i>[I've seen your report. I ordered the crown prince to Luoyang to inspect around counties for the damage for me.]</i>

183
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,359
Thanks a lot.

184
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:58,070
Please report for me.

185
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:00,479
Princess Yongan has been found in Luoyang.

186
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,280
She's fine.

187
00:15:01,950 --> 00:15:02,950
Please rest assured.

188
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:05,070
Yes.

189
00:16:05,390 --> 00:16:06,559
Forgive me, please.

190
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:08,190
I forgot you're...

191
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:11,949
I'll send some guards for you tomorrow.

192
00:16:11,950 --> 00:16:13,040
To protect you.

193
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,240
I came here for...

194
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:19,599
I'll come tomorrow.

195
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,400
Wait.

196
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:21,999
It's late now.

197
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:23,799
You must come here for an emergency.

198
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:24,600
Yes.

199
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:29,069
I just received a handwritten letter from his Majesty from Chang'an.

200
00:16:29,070 --> 00:16:30,270
Please have a look.

201
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:34,839
His Highness has left Chang'an to inspect the damage

202
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,510
to show grace on behalf of His Majesty.

203
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:40,239
He'd arrive in a few days.

204
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:42,749
Thank you for delivering the letter, Mr. Hao.

205
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:44,040
I'll read it latter.

206
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,240
In that case,

207
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,830
I won't hurry to go back.

208
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:51,750
The crown prince is young and naughty.

209
00:16:52,270 --> 00:16:54,479
I have to look after him.

210
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:56,269
I can help you with that.

211
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:58,950
But... I've decided it.

212
00:16:59,710 --> 00:17:02,390
You have to stay with me in Luoyang for a while, Mr. Hao.

213
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:06,600
Princess, you've changed a lot.

214
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:11,280
What happened is a mixed blessing.

215
00:17:11,910 --> 00:17:13,310
I lost, I gained.

216
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:17,070
Now I know what Father often said to me.

217
00:17:17,910 --> 00:17:20,550
People live hard. How can we stand by?

218
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,600
I'm his daughter.

219
00:17:24,670 --> 00:17:26,760
How can I stay ignorant?

220
00:17:27,710 --> 00:17:30,430
You've suffered a great deal, haven't you?

221
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:32,880
I met many difficulties,

222
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:36,550
and many people to express my gratitude as well.

223
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,950
Difficulties will be gone,

224
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:45,000
but the gratitude will be< cherished in heart forever.

225
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:50,950
In the past, I only saw people's appearance.

226
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:55,240
Now I know I need to see what's in their mind.

227
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:59,760
Someone seems kind but hides a malicious heart.

228
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:04,670
Someone has a cold face but a kind heart.

229
00:18:07,030 --> 00:18:08,400
Just like you, Mr. Hao.

230
00:19:18,319 --> 00:19:19,679
Why can't I master it?

231
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:22,038
Your Tao is different.

232
00:19:22,039 --> 00:19:23,079
You can't do it.

233
00:19:23,719 --> 00:19:24,918
Give up now.

234
00:19:24,919 --> 00:19:25,880
Different Tao?

235
00:19:27,199 --> 00:19:28,520
Where's the difference?

236
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:35,120
<i>In your opinion, what's my reason to defend Shuozhou?</i>

237
00:19:36,039 --> 00:19:40,280
<i>Fights or surrenders are just the means</i>

238
00:19:40,959 --> 00:19:43,678
<i>to guarantee the citizens stay away from war and live a happy life.</i>

239
00:19:43,679 --> 00:19:45,000
<i>These are the most important.</i>

240
00:19:45,799 --> 00:19:49,760
<i>This is the Tao I stick to.</i>

241
00:20:05,319 --> 00:20:06,919
What's exactly my Tao is?

242
00:20:12,559 --> 00:20:13,798
Senior Qin.

243
00:20:13,799 --> 00:20:15,599
Did Yuan fall asleep?

244
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:16,159
Yes.

245
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:16,960
Okay.

246
00:20:18,199 --> 00:20:20,599
We asked Luo Shiba to share messages with us.

247
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:23,838
But when we sent the message, she never wrote back.

248
00:20:23,839 --> 00:20:27,678
Now she suddenly wanted to see us and would bring a friend to us.

249
00:20:27,679 --> 00:20:28,760
A friend?

250
00:20:30,520 --> 00:20:32,678
We have no progress so far.

251
00:20:32,679 --> 00:20:37,839
Maybe this friend can bring some messages of Young Master.

252
00:20:45,959 --> 00:20:47,600
Luo Shiba, here you are.

253
00:20:48,559 --> 00:20:49,839
Your friend is...

254
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:55,558
Luo Shiba.

255
00:20:55,559 --> 00:20:57,120
This is your friend?

256
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:02,240
Everyone listen, kill Ashile Sun to take revenge on the governor.

257
00:21:04,199 --> 00:21:04,999
Wait.

258
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:15,640
About Gongsun Heng, I have a clear conscience.

259
00:21:16,600 --> 00:21:18,279
Now Changge is missing.

260
00:21:18,280 --> 00:21:21,239
I come here only to find her.

261
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,280
Find her?

262
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,718
It's you who took her to the grassland

263
00:21:24,719 --> 00:21:26,439
where she encountered the misery, isn't it?

264
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,798
Luo Shiba.

265
00:21:28,799 --> 00:21:31,399
You don't know what Ashile Tribe means to us, do you?

266
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,838
How can you bring him to Tang?

267
00:21:32,839 --> 00:21:33,880
I only want to find her.

268
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:37,879
I'll find a way to find her even without your help.

269
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:38,680
You...

270
00:21:39,760 --> 00:21:41,198
Ashile Sun.

