00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,839
Be a man, brother,

556
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,838
like our father.

557
00:35:23,839 --> 00:35:25,120
Win the trust from our people.

558
00:35:25,640 --> 00:35:27,160
And be a wise emperor.

559
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,160
Hao Du.

560
00:35:52,640 --> 00:35:54,998
You found Leyan first.

561
00:35:54,999 --> 00:35:55,799
Thank you.

562
00:35:57,999 --> 00:36:00,600
Have you accompanied her all the time?

563
00:36:01,720 --> 00:36:02,680
What do you mean?

564
00:36:03,759 --> 00:36:04,559
Nothing.

565
00:36:05,079 --> 00:36:06,239
I just felt regretful.

566
00:36:06,799 --> 00:36:08,838
If I hadn't been recalled by his Majesty,

567
00:36:08,839 --> 00:36:11,799
I might have been the one who found Leyan.

568
00:36:12,839 --> 00:36:14,679
Does that matter?

569
00:36:14,680 --> 00:36:15,880
It matters between you and me.

570
00:36:18,640 --> 00:36:20,759
Is this because of Li Changge?

571
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:24,439
Protect the crown prince.

572
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:26,359
Don't lose his Highness again.

573
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,160
Hao Du.

574
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:29,640
Leyan wouldn't been left alone in the stage

575
