587
00:37:14,680 --> 00:37:16,879
I've checked her for several times, but she kept staring

588
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:17,959
at the writing on the wall.

589
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:19,479
She hasn't moved at all.

590
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:22,700
Is there something wrong with her?

591
00:37:23,839 --> 00:37:24,919
Look at her.

592
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:26,200
She is just so stubborn.

593
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:30,199
I've told her she couldn't make it, she just didn't listen.

594
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:31,039
I'll check her out.

595
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:35,519
Good to see you, Mr. Situ.

596
00:37:36,799 --> 00:37:37,599
Master.

597
00:37:38,479 --> 00:37:40,759
Can I talk to her?

598
00:37:47,020 --> 00:37:52,460
<i>[Non-interference]</i>

599
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,720
The night you came,

600
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:09,200
I was just passing by.

601
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:12,839
I saw you practicing swordsmanship in the middle of the night.

602
00:38:13,799 --> 00:38:19,680
You've stayed in the silence room ever since you came to our temple.

603
00:38:20,920 --> 00:38:22,479
Do you have any thoughts?

604
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:25,720
I've been taught by my teacher since childhood.

605
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:28,799
I've read books from all classes of authors.

606
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,520
I've never liked the thought of non-interference of Taoism.

607
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:35,920
To struggle with people, you can find your refuge.

608
00:38:37,079 --> 00:38:40,319
To struggle with people, you can achieve your pursuit.

609
00:38:42,239 --> 00:38:43,360
For all these years,

610
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:45,799
I've held a strong belief in it.

611
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:48,880
But in these few days,

612
00:38:49,999 --> 00:38:51,200
I started to realize that

613
00:38:53,160 --> 00:38:54,120
I was wrong.

614
00:38:57,519 --> 00:38:58,519
If I hadn't struggled,

615
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:04,500
someone like my real brother wouldn't have died for me.

616
00:39:07,799 --> 00:39:08,720
If I hadn't struggled,

617
00:39:09,799 --> 00:39:10,679
someone who has treated me like his daughter

618
00:39:10,680 --> 00:39:13,800
wouldn't have been died for me.

619
00:39:15,319 --> 00:39:16,200
If I hadn't struggled,

620
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:21,750
someone who has given all he got to me wouldn't have been in danger,

621
00:39:25,079 --> 00:39:26,400
while his dear family

622
00:39:27,839 --> 00:39:29,319
wouldn't have died for me as well.

623
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:35,720
One senior saved my life,

624
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:39,079
and taught me to find my own Tao.

625
00:39:40,239 --> 00:39:41,479
Non-interference.

626
00:39:43,120 --> 00:39:44,279
This is the way.

627
00:39:47,039 --> 00:39:48,440
God bless us all.

628
00:39:49,079 --> 00:39:53,479
If you really think in this way, you've spent some good time

629
00:39:54,279 --> 00:39:57,278
in this silence room.

630
00:39:57,279 --> 00:39:58,759
What about now?

631
00:40:01,079 --> 00:40:03,279
Dead people are gone forever.

632
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:06,160
I've wasted so much time on this.

633
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:10,719
It's really precious for us to be enlightened.

634
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:14,199
There are lots of refugees in Luoyang.

635
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:16,559
We're busy in helping those in need.

636
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:19,039
If you have time,

637
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:23,239
you can help me and Taoist Sun.

638
00:40:23,839 --> 00:40:26,319
Everything in Taoism is about people.

639
00:40:27,319 --> 00:40:29,120
We should appreciate the world we live in.

640
00:40:29,839 --> 00:40:31,200
Dwelling in the past

641
00:40:31,720 --> 00:40:34,079
will only bring you more troubles.

642
00:40:45,540 --> 00:40:48,420
